{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC12_KYL_080.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x17,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "*sigh* This is so relaxing..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "You're right. I've never been to such a relaxing tavern before."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "It feels a little weird to drink delicious tea at a tavern."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Since I can't drink alcohol, I've tried really hard to excel at other things. I hope you can see that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I recommend this fragranced black tea."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I tried it before. The fragrance is really sweet, but it tastes just like normal tea."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "That's the good thing about it. It'd be too much if tasted sweet, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Oh, really? I think the sweeter it is, the tastier it is."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x194,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "No, no, you're supposed to enjoy how savory the tea is. It'd be boring if it smelled and tasted sweet."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "That's not true. I think sweet teas are the best."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I agree. Sweet things are also good for recovering from fatigue, and they make you feel peaceful."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x141,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Two against one!? Am I wrong here!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x143,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I still can't agree, but if you like sweets, I have something good for you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "A baked good that's as sweet as can be. It's as sweet as a newlywed couple."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1b4,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Wow, thank you!<CR>*munch* *munch* *munch*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1b6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "...It might be a little too sweet..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, it is too sweet. That's all you can really taste..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x141,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Huh!? Didn't you just say the sweeter it is, the better!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "That's the tricky part. I also don't want to gain weight."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "You're right. Having something too sweet will just make you tired."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x143,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "That's not what you said a moment ago! Aren't you contradicting yourself!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "It may seem like a contradiction,<CR>but it's not. That's what makes<CR>sweets so mysterious..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x110,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...I can't agree with any of this..."
        }
    ]
}